# CRUD Pattern

## Default surface

**List-first**: searchable table or card grid + primary “Create” CTA.

| Action | UI |
|--------|-----|
| Create / Edit master record | Modal / dialog (`*FormDialog`, `StandardModal`, `EntityFormDialog`) |
| Quick create beside list | Narrow side panel (~20–24rem); table stays primary |
| Multiple entity tables on one page | Tabs — never stack unrelated tables |
| Delete / irreversible | Confirm dialog |
| Import | Upload → parse → preview table → confirm |

## Server flow

```
UI → action (guard + revalidate) → service (rules) → repository (DB)
```

## Client feedback

- `useTransition` / pending disables submit
- Toast success/error (sonner) OR `{ ok }` result handling — match the module
- Revalidate list paths after writes

## URL state (when repo already uses it)

`?create=` / `?edit=id` for deep-linkable dialogs. Follow local convention; don’t invent a second state system.

## Empty states

Real empty copy + CTA. Never seed fake demo rows in production UI.
